---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="NotionStack's Privacy Policy - How we collect, use, and protect your information"
>
  <div class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last Updated: January 12, 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>NotionStack ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website notionstack.so.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3>2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <p>We do not currently collect personal information directly from users. If we implement features requiring user accounts or contact forms in the future, we will update this policy accordingly.</p>

        <h3>2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p>When you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information about your device, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Operating system</li>
          <li>IP address</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
          <li>Referring website addresses</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.3 Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
        <p>We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and maintain our website</li>
          <li>Analyze website usage and improve our services</li>
          <li>Monitor and prevent fraudulent activity</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Affiliate Relationships</h2>
        <p>NotionStack participates in affiliate marketing programs. When you click on affiliate links and make purchases, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps support our platform.</p>
        <p>Affiliate links may redirect through third-party services (such as Gumroad) that have their own privacy policies. We recommend reviewing their policies before making purchases.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites and services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to read their privacy policies.</p>

        <h3>Third-Party Services We Use:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Netlify:</strong> Website hosting and deployment</li>
          <li><strong>Gumroad:</strong> Affiliate link tracking and redirects</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>The right to access your personal information</li>
          <li>The right to correct inaccurate information</li>
          <li>The right to request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>The right to opt-out of certain data uses</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our website is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through the information available on our website.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
  }

  .container {
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding: 2rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
